===========================

6-31++G Split Valence Basis
---------------------------

The 6-31++G basis set adds a diffuse (s,p) shell to elements Li - Cl and a
single diffuse s to hydrogen.
The 6-31G basis set uses 6 Gaussians to expand the 1s core of second period
elements.
